<h2>What Are FreeCell?</h2>
<p>FreeCell is a wonderful, online version of Solitaire that you can enjoy on your computer or tablet without needing to download anything. You'll play with a standard deck of 52 cards and have four special "free cells" at the top of your screen. These free cells allow you to temporarily park cards, helping you organize and build up four foundation piles—from Ace to King—one for each suit.</p>
<p>The best part about FreeCell is that almost every deal can be solved, giving you endless new challenges as you practice planning your moves and discovering winning strategies. With its simple rules and bright, colorful design, FreeCell is an excellent way for kids to have fun while learning to think ahead with online card games.</p>
